net: thunderbolt: fix memory leak in tbnet_open()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.13 by commit ed6e955f3b7e0e622c080f4bcb5427a5e1af4c2a, it was introduced in version v5.13 by commit 180b0689425c6fb2b35e69a3316ee38371a782df. For more details please see the references link.
